Class Municipality

java.lang.Object
Models.Municipality
All Implemented Interfaces:
Region
Direct Known Subclasses:
MockedMunicipality
@Layer(BACK_END) public class Municipality extends Object implements Region
The Municipality class represents a municipality within a district. It contains a list of parishes and provides methods to manage them. This class implements the Region interface.
